                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "buy_tm_swordsdance_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Back to the counter",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "OPEN_DEFAULT_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "back_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Goodbye",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "goodbye_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Three badges. The glass opens. These are the machines that decide matches — setup, coverage, the moves a leader would rather you did not carry into the rematch. Same eight-use burn, same no-repair. Choose like it is the last disc in the falls, because on a bad week it is."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Mika — the glass cabinet",
                    Label: "tm_master"
                },
                {
                    Priority: -1,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Back to the counter",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "OPEN_DEFAULT_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "back_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Goodbye",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "goodbye_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "The League says coil fatigue — eight castings and the lattice gives. I say the disc finishes saying what it knows. Kenji at the museum calls that romanticizing a capacitor. Kenji dusts bones for a living."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I have seen a disc give its eighth teaching in the middle of a losing streak and land like a first. Whatever is in there spends itself all the way down. Respect the last use. Plan for it."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Mika — why discs die",
                    Label: "burnout_lore"
                }
            ]
        },
